  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/481aaf3aeca7ee6a73b6dafdb372bc1e.poster.avif?t=1705926037\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/481aaf3aeca7ee6a73b6dafdb372bc1e.webm?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/481aaf3aeca7ee6a73b6dafdb372bc1e.mp4?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take part in exciting kart races in Kart Life!</strong><br>You can compete in exciting and challenging races with players from all over the world, upgrade your racing karts, train your agility and concentration to win. Well, start your engines and let's go!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/05c735a8d6c6736bd570477b5fb6202b.poster.avif?t=1705926037\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/05c735a8d6c6736bd570477b5fb6202b.webm?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/05c735a8d6c6736bd570477b5fb6202b.mp4?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore race tracks!</strong><br>Master challenging tracks to improve your skills and leave your opponents behind. Knowing how to enter corners correctly will make you truly unbeatable. Upgrade your kart to do even better!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/4541cd2ef790cac0ab1764fe3dce3613.poster.avif?t=1705926037\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/4541cd2ef790cac0ab1764fe3dce3613.webm?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/4541cd2ef790cac0ab1764fe3dce3613.mp4?t=1705926037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Challenge players from all over the world!</strong><br>Experience breathtaking action, lightning fast speed and intense competition. Let luck and speed come your way! Download now and start your quest for karting glory!<br><strong> Kart Life - Where speed meets skill and champions are born.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492910/extras/2526af5a00942c9fc3912f3b83671871.avif?t=1705926037\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Intense kart racing with high-speed action;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Upgradable karts with unique characteristics;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Online multiplayer;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Masterful controls for precise maneuvering;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Stunning visuals and immersive sound;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Experience the adrenaline rush of kart racing;</strong><br></li><li><strong> Become a karting legend in the exciting world of Kart Life.</strong> </li></ul>",
